snippet: The Vagos Outlaw Motorcycle Gang was dealt a major blow on Thursday, with a series of raids throughout Southern California that led to the arrests of 12 members and the seizure of more than 300 guns.
lead_paragraph: The Vagos Outlaw Motorcycle Gang was dealt a major blow on Thursday, with a series of raids throughout Southern California that led to the arrests of 12 members and the seizure of more than 300 guns.

headline.main: In California, Raid on Gang Members Leads to 12 Arrests
